views.text:
Are you a crypto enthusiast? Interested in bitcoin? Curious about the crypto market? HODL is your one-stop for trading crypto & stocks. Get real-time data at your fingertips! With stand-out features unlike other crypto trading apps, HODL offers various charts to interpret market data & helps you analyze your portfolio at a glance. And the best thing is, you have access to real-time prices & data from 240+ global exchanges & relevant crypto news in just a few clicks! 
Get the latest market news on all things crypto & stocks from multiple reputed aggregators at your fingertips. 
Catch up on all the buzz around crypto news with exclusive filtered & blended tweets from Twitter, Stocktwits, HODL in real-time! With exclusive insight, invest decisively & confidently.
A simple crypto tracker, simplifies trading for you.
Get your hands on simple navigation, customizable charts & seamless wallet integrations with various crypto exchanges such as Binance. 
Never lose track of your holdings with all your crypto investments secure in one place on HODL! Make the best use of extensive trading tools like the crypto screeners, watchlists, customizable price alerts & portfolio manager, in the all-in-one-crypto app - HODL
Struggling with multiple crypto apps for trading & tracking? Wade through the volatile market, empowered with HODL’s all-in-one multifunctional stock & crypto portfolio management tools. Get key information instantly & invest smartly! 
Install HODL, your one-stop-crypto app! 
Don’t miss out on anything crypto anymore! 
GET REAL-TIME DATA FROM ALL (240+) GLOBAL EXCHANGES
Smart & intuitive crypto tracker 
Instant alerts from all exchanges 
No crypto news missed! 
KEEP UP WITH CRYPTO NEWS WITH ALERTS 
News from multiple aggregators, streamed in real-time, all in one place!
Intuitive crypto tracker at hand.
Broader & faster real-time coverage
More relevant news coverage
DISCOVER BLENDED & FILTERED IN-APP SOCIAL MEDIA:
Filtered & blended from Twitter, Stocktwits & HODL
Curated & relevant coverage of crypto tweets 

TRADE SMARTER & STRESS-FREE:
Make trading decisions without any of the stress with these key features: 
CHARTS: 
Use customizable time units, ranges, chart types & indicators 
Distill the signal from the noise with simple charts 
Analyze & understand the patterns within the visual data 
PRICE ALERTS: 
Set intelligent alerts whenever a threshold for price/percentage is crossed.
SMART ALERT BRACKETS: 
Let HODL reset price alert targets for you
Not sure what alert to set? UseHODL’s AI-led alerts 
ALL CRYPTO SCREENER: 
Browse trending coins like top gainers & losers
Understand pattern & predict better 
WATCHLIST & PORTFOLIO TRACKER
Keep an eye out for trending coins 
Watchlist your favorites 
Simple crypto tracker & portfolio management
COIN PROFILES: 
Understand your crypto better by tapping on a coin name & get historical insight 
WALLET INTEGRATION:
Auto-sync your portfolio with any ERC20 wallet
Ensure all your orders are synced in one place
Share & collaborate on portfolios

Some of the supported exchanges: 
Bit2C, BitBank, BitexBook, Bitfinex, BitFlip, bitFlyer, bitFlyerFX, BitGrail, Bithumb, Bitlish, BitMarket, BitMart, Bitso, Bitstamp, BitTrex, Bleutrade, LocalBitcoins, Luno, Lykke, MonetaGo, Nebula, Neraex, Novaexchange, OKCoin,Surbitcoin, etc

Unlock the potential of crypto with the best cryptocurrency tracker & exclusive insights. Get unlimited access for free on HODL! Ready to invest in crypto? Download HODL today!
